  <notes-results date="2026-06-26">
    Option (b) inline citation correction applied. Changes in `docs/architecture/rag-architecture.md`:
    - Top intro: removed misattributed ADR-014 cite for tenant isolation; added FR-06 pending-decision callout section explaining drift + owner's optional path-(a) alternative.
